		<dc:creator><![CDATA[liza]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>About Liza</h2>
Welcome to Liza — a beautifully crafted blog theme. Whether you are a lifestyle blogger, a traveler, or a food enthusiast, Liza provides you with a stunning canvas for your stories.

<h3>Our Mission</h3>
We believe every story deserves to look beautiful. That's why we designed Liza with attention to detail, clean typography, and an elegant layout that puts your content first.

<h3>Features</h3>
<ul>
<li>Responsive and mobile-friendly design</li>
<li>Featured slider with stunning visuals</li>
<li>Multiple layout options</li>
<li>Dark mode support</li>
<li>Full customizer integration</li>
</ul>]]></content:encoded>
